{"tid":1088739,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"VR技術重播車路士問題球 加歷查親證助理裁判視線受阻","createTime":"2019-04-02T09:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T17:50:04.000Z","uid":32938,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"77bdbff5dc88f6f36df268a26b58ee84a3fed87d","tid":1088739,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2019/04/20190402_Jamie-Carragher_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2019%2F04%2F20190402_Jamie-Carragher_2.jpg&h=4180c844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《天空體育》的足球節目《Monday Night Football》在最新一集中，亦再有研究這球問題球，節目的主持之一加歷查則提出一項新觀點，指旁證或因被韋利安阻擋視線，並透過VR模擬當時旁證的視點，證明旁證的視線或受韋利安所影響，而未能看到在越位位置的艾斯派古達。<br />\n<br />\n加歷查指旁證在該情況下，未能判斷為越位亦是情有可原，更向他表示同情，「旁證的視線確實受到韋利安的影響，在球賽進行的電光火石的一剎那，他根本難以在當刻下判斷。我並非為球證而辯護，而是旁證在當刻被阻，未有任何表示是合理的做法，所以我對球證感到難過，我們需要易地而處，球證亦絕對有他們的難處。」"},{"pid":"b4c9d9489ecca2a48f1c453b1611661d5849376a","tid":1088739,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"不愧係黑世三 出完波再做人牆"},{"pid":"68816358324fdc9a69ae29feeb7048853750921c","tid":1088739,"uid":216709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFIq5UPA-JM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKFIq5UPA-JM&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=63a9691f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFIq5UPA-JM</a>"},{"pid":"afb929a626b2fe0a8d6f1c563d57922f85da76ba","tid":1088739,"uid":53238,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"VAR 都破解埋<br />\n做黑世一都唔過份"},{"pid":"b78efa6ec23ab2c9327ecab8d12d003aa5451234","tid":1088739,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"JC都係專心講波算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal